data.title: John Sparrow David Thompson Facts for Kids
data.meta_description: John Sparrow David Thompson facts. Sir John Sparrow David Thompson  (November 10, 1845 – December 12, 1894) was the 4th Prime Minister of Canada. He served from November 24, 1892 until his death from a heart attack on December 12, 1894.
data.text: Sir John Sparrow David Thompson (November 10, 1845 – December 12, 1894) was the 4th Prime Minister of Canada. He served from November 24, 1892 until his death from a heart attack on December 12, 1894.
